<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Chinook_Jargon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span></h2>
<div class="infobox sisterproject">
